Package: intersectr
Type: Package
Title: Spatiotemporal Intersections
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: person("David", "Blodgett", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "dblodgett@usgs.gov")
Depends:
    R (>= 3.0)
Description: Package for intersecting spatiotemporal attribute data. The primary 
    emphasis is on gridded time-series data such as meteorological forcings that 
    need to be intersected with a spatial modeling mesh or set of spatial modeling units.
URL: https://github.com/dblodgett-usgs/intersectr
BugReports: https://github.com/dblodgett-usgs.intersectr/issues
Imports: sf, stars, dplyr, RNetCDF, ncmeta
Remotes: hypertidy/ncmeta, r-spatial/stars, r-spatial/sf 
Suggests: testthat, tibble, ncdfgeom, knitr, rmarkdown
License: CC0
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 6.1.1
